\b\fs26 \cf0 Notes
\b0\fs24 \
* Files/folders whose name begins with underscore \'93_\'94 will not be displayed in script menu. Thus, you can use them for setting files, library scripts etc.\
* You can line up the menu items in numerical order by adding \'93number + closing parenthesis ())\'94 at the head of the file name.\
The part \'93number + )\'94 and the file extension won't be shown in the menu.\
\
