\b \cf0 Sample Scripts
\b0 \
On the first launch, CotEditor copies SampleScript folder that contains some of sample scripts for CotEditor into ScriptMenu folder.  If you want to copy it later, select hidden \'94Copy Sample to Scripts Folder" menu item in the Script menu  (press option key to display it).\
